      • validate

        boolean validate()
                 throws IbanException
        Validates a IBAN

      • toString

        String toString()
        Returns the string representation of the IBAN
        Overrides:
        toString in class Object
        Returns:
        The IBAN in the format "country-code|checkdigit|bank-ident|kto-ident", for example "DE62701500000020228888"

      • getBic

        Get the BIC refers to the IBAN
        Returns:
